Date: Mon, 1 Jun 2020 07:21:38 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 10/27] net: phy: Enable wake on PHY activity for Marvell PHY

This commit add support to "wake on PHY activity" WoL feature by
enabling link state change interrupt.

Signed-off-by: Song, Yoong Siang <yoong.siang.song@intel.com>
---
